<br>
Of the casters, necros rule.  Lifetaps, nasty DOTs, shadow step, and a very nasty pet that some classes can't easily neutralize.  Wizards and druids can also be pretty nasty when well played or getting first strike.<br>
<br>
And nobody will beat a well played bard in an big outdoor zone.  It may take the bard forever to win, but they shouldn't ever loose a war of attrition.<br>
